That's why I'm personally asking for your help today: Will you give $15 or more now so we can hit our mid-month goal, win in GA & defend our Senate majority? bit.ly/3qolzy5 - Rev. Warnock

That is not what I stand for, and it is not what America stands for. I call on ALL Americans to help ease tensions and calm tempers. Thank You."
